    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "those are good high-level points. can you expand on the 'national sovereignty' and 'rule of law' aspects specifically? like, how do proponents argue that a lack of control over borders fundamentally undermines the legitimacy of a government? i want my kids to be able to explain the philosophical connection between borders and state authority.",
